# zice-frontend

- App Router under `src/app/`; use Server Components unless the page needs client interactivity.
- API calls go through `src/lib/api/client.ts` with the user's JWT — no service keys in the browser.
- Tenant: respect `src/middleware.ts`; pass org context via headers the backend expects.
- Styling: Tailwind only; icons via Lucide.
- Roster Auditor: client-side only — do not upload CSV roster data to the server.
- New admin pages: reuse `src/components/admin/DataTable`, soft-delete/restore components.

Repo `AGENTS.md` (after `make sync-agent-docs`) lists routes and env vars.
